246
00:13:49,680 --> 00:13:51,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Wir brauchen Ingwer, fein gewürfelt,</font>

247
00:13:51,960 --> 00:13:54,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Zitronengras in feinen Scheibchen,</font>

248
00:13:54,120 --> 00:13:56,560
<font color=#FFFF00>jungen Knoblauch,</font>
